Package: meshSDM
Type: Package
Title: 3 Dimensional Species Distribution Models
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Adam M. Wilson <adamw@buffalo.edu>
Maintainer: Adam M. Wilson <adamw@buffalo.edu>
Description: Set of functions to assist in building species distribution models on 3D mesh. Designed to process fine grain (~1mm resolution) topographic meshes of coral reef environments and prepare data for distribution modelling using models such as Maxent. This is in 'alpha' state - not all functions are working correctly.  Use at your own risk.
